## 5. Icon System

### Primary Icons Used

**Navigation & Actions:**

- 🎓 Graduation Cap (Students, Education)
- 💼 Briefcase (Companies, Jobs)
- 🌙 Moon (Dark mode toggle)
- ☀️ Sun (Light mode toggle)
- 🔍 Search/Magnifying Glass
- ➕ Plus (Add new)
- ✏️ Pencil/Edit (Edit profile)
- 👁️ Eye (View details)
- 📤 Send/Paper plane (Apply)
- 📄 Document (CV/Files)
- ⬆️ Upload (File upload)

**Information & Metadata:**

- 📍 Pin/Map marker (Location)
- ⏰ Clock (Duration)
- 📅 Calendar (Dates, deadlines)

**Statistics:**

- 👥 Users/People (Applications, students)
- 📈 Trending up (Growth, stats)
- 👁️ Eye (Views, shortlisted)

**Status Indicators:**

- ✓ Checkmark (Success, active)
- ✗ X mark (Rejected, closed)
- ⚠️ Warning (Attention needed)

