## 7. Spacing System

### Padding/Margin Scale

- **XS**: 0.25rem (4px)
- **SM**: 0.5rem (8px)
- **MD**: 1rem (16px)
- **LG**: 1.5rem (24px)
- **XL**: 2rem (32px)
- **2XL**: 3rem (48px)
- **3XL**: 4rem (64px)
- **4XL**: 5rem (80px)

### Container Max Widths

- **Content**: 1280px
- **Form Sections**: 640px
- **Cards**: Full width within grid

